ursday morning, Nov. 19, and then waited=C2=A0six days=C2=A0to put in a buy=
 order for those 200 shares, and those orders traded with each other.
  [3]
=C2=A0It is a more=C2=A0leisurely pace. Nobody traded any Hometown stock at=
