s crossed. Bloomberg tells me that those 200 shares are the only shares tha=
t traded the whole week of Nov. 23. The whole month of November 2020, only =
1,070 shares traded.
Were all of them wash trades among these alleged conspirators? Man, I don=
=E2=80=99t know, but would=C2=A0you=C2=A0buy incredibly illiquid shares of =
a money-losing deli at a $100 million market cap? The reason that the SEC a=
