s minutes or hours or days apart, is that no one was trading Hometown stock=
=C2=A0except=C2=A0these alleged conspirators. Or almost no one. The SEC doe=
s say:
However, certain individual investors not associated with Defendants also p=
urchased shares of Hometown International at the artificially inflated pric=
