It doesn=E2=80=99t say who though, or how many, or when. And there is no al=
legation at all that the defendants=C2=A0tried=C2=A0to get anyone else to b=
uy the stock. They were not pumping it on message boards, telling people th=
at Hometown had discovered the next great sandwich. They were just building=
