0 of real money =E2=80=94=C2=A0which you=E2=80=99re sending to yourself any=
way =E2=80=94=C2=A0into $83 million of paper value.=C2=A0
What do you do with that paper value? I mean, reading between the lines, I =
gather that the answer is that you go to Manoj Jain and you say =E2=80=9Chi=
, we have a $100 million-ish public company, we hear that you have a $400 m=
