  [4]
=C2=A0The value that you=E2=80=99re putting in is fake =E2=80=94=C2=A0you=
=E2=80=99ve got a small money-losing deli and some $2,000 wash trades =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0but everything that we=E2=80=99re talking about here is pretty =
fake anyway so maybe it=E2=80=99s fine?=C2=A0
Now, the deli is famous =E2=80=94=C2=A0much more famous than E-Waste or=C2=
=A0other reverse-merger shell companies =E2=80=94=C2=A0largely because (1) =
it=E2=80=99s a deli, which is funny and (2) David Einhorn called attention =
to it in his=C2=A0investor letter. This was in=C2=A0the glory days of meme =
