 equating the side gig with some sort of midlife crisis. Some advisers told=
 him to hang it up. =E2=80=9CI thought for a minute, Well, can I do this, c=
an I not do this?=E2=80=9D recalls Solomon, who donates the proceeds from h=
is gigs and Spotify plays to drug-addiction-related philanthropies. (He say=
s the total he has raised is in the six figures.) Those doubts soon dispers=
